<i>noun</i>: 성냥갑 [성냥깝] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>성냥갑 [성냥깝]</dt><br>
<dd>matchbox</dd><br>
<dd>성냥을 그어 불을 일으킬 수 있도록 옆면에 거친 부분이 있는, 성냥이 담긴 작은 상자.</dd><br>
<dd>A small box with matches that has a rough side that is used to strike matches on in order to ignite the match.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>